because we now want to bridge and-- into

00:00:30.690 --> 00:00:33.380
the deeper questions
surrounding reincarnation,

00:00:33.410 --> 00:00:38.420
the deeper perspective.
Where is reincarnation taking humanity?

00:00:38.450 --> 00:00:43.260
Where is this constantly learning
and recycling and recycling,

00:00:43.290 --> 00:00:45.500
creating new and new platforms

00:00:45.530 --> 00:00:48.500
in our incarnational experience
- where is it going?

