that - I'm sure you relate to that, Chris.

00:02:54.850 --> 00:02:58.540
It's quite hard to hold it because
it's-- not everyone else has it.

00:02:58.560 --> 00:02:59.880
And so

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:04.300
it puts you-- it puts me in a-- I'm more

00:03:04.330 --> 00:03:10.300
relaxed than most people I know
at a fundamental level, because

00:03:10.330 --> 00:03:14.200
I have this knowing
that everything's going to be fine.

