00:32:19.970 --> 00:32:22.940
We've never had anything happen in history

00:32:22.970 --> 00:32:25.500
which is comparable
to what's coming at us now.

00:32:25.530 --> 00:32:29.810
Because when we've had hurricanes or great
natural disasters, they've always affected

00:32:29.840 --> 00:32:32.660
one part of the world,
but not the other part of the world.

00:32:32.690 --> 00:32:37.860
But the global systems crisis that seems
to be imminent, being driven by a global

00:32:37.890 --> 00:32:42.020
ecological crisis,
is going to affect all continents,

00:32:42.050 --> 00:32:44.310
all people, all places.

00:32:44.510 --> 00:32:47.160
That's going to push humanity

00:32:47.440 --> 00:32:49.860
into a different experiential field.

00:32:49.890 --> 00:32:52.380
And the point here is that the collective

00:32:52.410 --> 00:32:56.940
psyche is going to be energised
by all of this disruption.

00:32:56.970 --> 00:32:59.780
It literally is going to begin to boil

00:32:59.810 --> 00:33:02.940
underneath us, underneath our
individual minds.

00:33:02.970 --> 00:33:07.240
And my understanding
of what's happening is

00:33:07.280 --> 00:33:11.420
that in evolution there are, kind of,

00:33:11.450 --> 00:33:15.380
multiple levels of evolution, at least,
say, two levels of evolution.

00:33:15.410 --> 00:33:18.540
We and I are being born
over and over again.

00:33:18.570 --> 00:33:22.140
We're born for 100 years at a time -
we live 100 years, 100 years.

00:33:22.170 --> 00:33:24.180
But underneath those 100 year cycles,

00:33:24.210 --> 00:33:28.500
there is a learning taking place, there is
a developmental process taking place.

00:33:28.530 --> 00:33:31.020
We usually refer to this as the soul.

00:33:31.050 --> 00:33:34.020
So the individual ego incarnates,

00:33:34.050 --> 00:33:39.180
but the soul is growing, becoming more,
becoming more, suffusing our lives.

00:33:39.210 --> 00:33:41.900
But the same thing happens collectively.

00:33:41.930 --> 00:33:44.540
Every generation, every generation,

00:33:44.560 --> 00:33:46.330
billions and billions of people are being

00:33:46.360 --> 00:33:50.338
born, but there is a learning
gathering underneath them,

00:33:50.538 --> 00:33:53.180
that is collecting all of their learning

00:33:53.210 --> 00:33:57.500
in these deep, deep,
collective archetypal structures.

00:33:57.530 --> 00:34:01.220
That's what's coming to boil,
not just our individual incarnation,

00:34:01.250 --> 00:34:05.330
but that underlying structures
coming into a high energy state.

00:34:05.360 --> 00:34:09.020
And I think it's coming to a state where

00:34:09.050 --> 00:34:11.420
the sheer energy of our suffering,

00:34:11.450 --> 00:34:16.690
the energy of our despair,
or the energy of our anxiety,

00:34:16.720 --> 00:34:20.460
is driving us to a breaking point

00:34:20.490 --> 00:34:25.500
where suddenly we're going to be flooded
with a different kind of common sense,

00:34:25.530 --> 00:34:28.940
a different common sense,
a different set of priorities,

00:34:28.970 --> 00:34:33.650
a different set of values,
a different experience of each other.

00:34:33.680 --> 00:34:35.540
The only way I think that we can

00:34:35.570 --> 00:34:41.320
go as far as we need to go in order
to save ourselves, and the planet

00:34:41.360 --> 00:34:45.540
in as little time as we have,
is to understand

00:34:45.570 --> 00:34:47.690
the dynamics of the collective

00:34:47.720 --> 00:34:51.740
unconscious,
the field-dynamics of consciousness and

00:34:51.770 --> 00:34:57.500
that-- how fields operate
in non-equilibrium systems.

00:34:57.530 --> 00:35:00.780
At least this is what
has come through my visionary experience,

00:35:00.810 --> 00:35:04.340
over and over,
that we are coming to a point where

00:35:04.370 --> 00:35:10.460
there is a crisis which builds
in intensity, until it looks like

00:35:10.490 --> 00:35:12.000
all is lost.

00:35:12.520 --> 00:35:16.920
So much disruption,
so much loss of control,

00:35:17.120 --> 00:35:18.440
so much

00:35:18.800 --> 00:35:22.320
death, challenged at a very deep level.

00:35:22.520 --> 00:35:25.160
But when it's at its worst

00:35:26.320 --> 00:35:28.200
it begins to pass.

00:35:28.280 --> 00:35:29.780
We pick ourselves up.

00:35:29.810 --> 00:35:33.980
We somehow rise to the
challenge of this crisis.

00:35:34.010 --> 00:35:35.940
And in rising to the challenge,

00:35:35.970 --> 00:35:40.740
we are changed, we are profoundly changed,
such that as we

00:35:40.770 --> 00:35:45.980
become-- start to come out of this period
of history, we find that what our nature,

00:35:46.010 --> 00:35:50.100
the nature that we are carrying,
its not just a different set of attitudes,

00:35:50.130 --> 00:35:57.060
not just a different set of beliefs,
but a fundamental-- a fundamentally new

00:35:57.090 --> 00:35:58.740
way of being conscious.

00:35:58.770 --> 00:36:02.940
A new organisation of our
consciousness emerges.

00:36:02.970 --> 00:36:05.420
Something has shifted in place.

00:36:05.450 --> 00:36:10.940
And we find that things which
were not easy are suddenly easy.

00:36:10.970 --> 00:36:14.820
Things which are out of reach
are suddenly within reach.

00:36:14.850 --> 00:36:19.100
Possibilities are emerging much faster
than we would have ever predicted.

00:36:19.130 --> 00:36:22.740
That's the type of transformation
I think we're looking at. A

00:36:22.760 --> 00:36:23.960
truly--

00:36:24.200 --> 00:36:27.020
a rebirth of humanity,

00:36:27.050 --> 00:36:31.560
so that-- in my work, I call it 'the
birth of the future human.' You know

00:36:31.720 --> 00:36:38.460
it's truly a demarcation of a different
kind of human being emerging.

00:36:38.480 --> 00:36:39.560
Now,

00:36:39.920 --> 00:36:42.420
I think our history is creating this.

00:36:42.450 --> 00:36:46.380
It's reincarnation, which is
coming to a phase of fruition.

00:36:46.410 --> 00:36:48.897
And I think we can get insights,

00:36:49.097 --> 00:36:54.260
or glimmers of what the future
will look like by looking at the great

00:36:54.290 --> 00:36:57.420
beings of our past, the great saints,
the great prophets,

00:36:57.450 --> 00:37:03.520
the great incarnations, the Christs,
the Buddhas, the prophets,

00:37:03.640 --> 00:37:10.130
those great beings who have always called
us into a higher order of existence.

00:37:10.160 --> 00:37:13.740
Those are prototypes, I think.
The prototypes which give us

00:37:13.770 --> 00:37:18.060
an inclination and an understanding
of what we are in the process of becoming

00:37:18.090 --> 00:37:22.130
as a species, collectively.
I think we are truly becoming

00:37:22.160 --> 00:37:27.500
a species of Christs,
a species of Buddhas, a species

00:37:27.530 --> 00:37:29.120
of prophets, you know,

00:37:29.600 --> 00:37:34.200
with that magnitude,
that tremendous scale of heart.

00:37:34.840 --> 00:37:39.120
I don't know how long it's going to
take us to make this transition.

00:37:39.440 --> 00:37:41.820
Clearly, the ecological crisis,

00:37:41.850 --> 00:37:46.500
which is fermenting, is a crisis that's
going to be deepening for generations.

00:37:46.530 --> 00:37:50.400
It will be at least three
generations, four generations

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:52.040
before we hit

00:37:52.240 --> 00:37:55.210
the peak of these-- of this crisis.

00:37:55.240 --> 00:37:56.940
But I think we will come through it.

00:37:56.970 --> 00:38:00.975
And I think we're not talking
thousands and thousands of years,

00:38:01.175 --> 00:38:04.980
we're talking-- we have to make
this within a few hundred years

00:38:05.000 --> 00:38:06.170
to make this transition.

00:38:06.200 --> 00:38:10.940
And I think the 21st century
is the key century

00:38:10.970 --> 00:38:17.280
of the unravelling - it is where we
make key choices that shape our future.

00:38:17.440 --> 00:38:19.380
And one of the other things that happens

00:38:19.410 --> 00:38:25.980
in non-equilibrium systems is that
individual changes, small changes

00:38:26.010 --> 00:38:28.460
can catapult into massive outcomes.

00:38:28.490 --> 00:38:29.820
So the butterfly,

00:38:29.850 --> 00:38:35.170
whose wing in China sets off a hurricane
across the planet - that metaphor

00:38:35.200 --> 00:38:39.960
that individuals who have
achieved within themselves

00:38:40.240 --> 00:38:44.960
something of what humanity
is aspiring to change

00:38:45.400 --> 00:38:48.720
for solving these large problems -

00:38:49.040 --> 00:38:53.880
the impact of individuals
increases exponentially

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:57.120
in non-equilibrium systems.

00:38:57.680 --> 00:38:58.340
So, just in contrast, if we look just

00:38:58.360 --> 00:39:00.900
to the past we say, 'Well,
the individual can't do anything.

00:39:00.930 --> 00:39:03.020
We're being overwhelmed by-- just

00:39:03.050 --> 00:39:07.690
it's overwhelming historical forces are
coming at us.' It's just the opposite.

00:39:07.720 --> 00:39:09.120
As things

00:39:09.200 --> 00:39:10.520
intensify,

00:39:10.640 --> 00:39:13.200
the individual becomes

00:39:13.280 --> 00:39:15.060
more significant, a more
significant player.

00:39:15.090 --> 00:39:18.020
So beings who achieve

00:39:18.050 --> 00:39:22.560
a wholeness within their person,
they achieve

00:39:22.960 --> 00:39:24.560
a robust

00:39:24.680 --> 00:39:30.380
soul-consciousness in their person,
have a tremendous catalysing effect

00:39:30.410 --> 00:39:34.200
on people around them,
coming to their own version

00:39:34.240 --> 00:39:36.120
of that deep experience

00:39:36.160 --> 00:39:37.400
as well.

00:39:38.920 --> 00:39:40.320
Thank you.

00:39:40.880 --> 00:39:44.880
I love listening to you,
when you go off on a transmission.

00:39:46.760 --> 00:39:48.480
I was thinking,

00:39:49.480 --> 00:39:51.360
you know, if you were to ask yourself

00:39:55.400 --> 00:39:56.340
what one thing-- if there was one thing

00:39:56.370 --> 00:39:59.680
that happened on this planet
that could change everything

00:40:00.200 --> 00:40:03.900
quickly overnight,
what might that one thing be?

00:40:03.920 --> 00:40:04.960
And

00:40:05.400 --> 00:40:07.560
inside me the answer

00:40:07.640 --> 00:40:12.360
was-- it is that for us to see
through the veil of death. You know,

00:40:12.920 --> 00:40:15.080
because the moment

00:40:15.120 --> 00:40:20.820
one person sees through the veil of death,
fear is no more, it just isn't.

00:40:20.850 --> 00:40:26.292
There is no fear
because that's where fear resides.

00:40:26.492 --> 00:40:28.640
So the intensification

00:40:28.680 --> 00:40:31.840
of the energy you're talking
about, the suffering,

00:40:32.320 --> 00:40:33.100
you know, the love,

00:40:33.130 --> 00:40:37.280
all of it pouring towards this one
kind of point, this-- you know,

00:40:39.440 --> 00:40:46.440
it's the only thing that has the power
to pierce that veil, that veil of death.

00:40:46.760 --> 00:40:49.853
And so what I would expect,

00:40:50.053 --> 00:40:53.060
and what I have sort of seen

00:40:53.090 --> 00:40:57.380
through the Gene Keys and through
my teachings and transmissions,

00:40:57.410 --> 00:40:59.690
is that more and more people

00:40:59.720 --> 00:41:01.680
will gradually,

00:41:01.760 --> 00:41:04.380
as this boiling takes place,

00:41:04.400 --> 00:41:05.480
experience

00:41:06.040 --> 00:41:07.920
their consciousness, you know,

00:41:09.520 --> 00:41:12.980
having the ability to transcend

00:41:13.010 --> 00:41:16.706
life, birth and death, that cycle of life,

00:41:16.906 --> 00:41:22.690
you know. And be able to-- that
consciousness will retain the memory

00:41:22.720 --> 00:41:25.120
between life, birth and death,

00:41:25.240 --> 00:41:26.946
and carry it across.

00:41:27.146 --> 00:41:29.760
And what that-- you know, because

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:33.980
that's pure awakening
and when a being has that layer-- that

00:41:34.010 --> 00:41:37.340
level of awakening,
and they're sitting there manifesting,

00:41:37.370 --> 00:41:40.520
or standing there just moving
around being who they are

00:41:40.840 --> 00:41:45.130
and that is being emanated,
it is electrifying.

00:41:45.160 --> 00:41:49.837
It's electrifying to anyone else,
it's catching, it's contagious.

00:41:50.037 --> 00:41:52.500
You know, the transmission of wisdom,

00:41:52.530 --> 00:41:56.340
and love, and awakening
is contagious, you know,

00:41:56.360 --> 00:41:57.500
most people will know this.

00:41:57.530 --> 00:42:04.340
You go near one of these beings and
you can feel it, it crackles in the air.

00:42:04.370 --> 00:42:07.560
And so the more and more

00:42:07.640 --> 00:42:11.880
that is occurring,
the more and more this veil

00:42:12.280 --> 00:42:14.160
of-- will be breaking down.

00:42:14.200 --> 00:42:16.020
And then fear will start to leave

00:42:16.050 --> 00:42:20.540
this planet gradually,
person-by-person, person-by-person,

00:42:20.570 --> 00:42:22.460
generation-by-generation.

00:42:22.490 --> 00:42:24.980
And I even believe

00:42:25.010 --> 00:42:28.260
deep inside myself that that will enable

00:42:28.290 --> 00:42:32.420
children to come through,
to be born, without

00:42:32.450 --> 00:42:34.100
the wound of humanity.

00:42:34.130 --> 00:42:36.120
You know, just be born awake, you know,

00:42:36.560 --> 00:42:37.920
and therefore

00:42:39.080 --> 00:42:41.060
not have those-- not have to
go through this journey.

00:42:41.090 --> 00:42:46.460
And, of course, those children are us,
those are our future vehicles,

00:42:46.490 --> 00:42:49.460
and they will be born
through those awakened ones.

00:42:49.490 --> 00:42:52.260
You know, because
if you have two awakened ones coming

00:42:52.290 --> 00:42:56.800
together to bring a child,
then you have a clear conduit.

00:42:57.880 --> 00:43:01.534
You know, and that's a vessel
that you might want to jump into,

00:43:01.734 --> 00:43:04.260
to experience, and then
more, and more of that.

00:43:04.290 --> 00:43:08.340
And that so, in a way,
you could almost perceive that that's how

00:43:08.370 --> 00:43:12.650
the awakened consciousness
will colonise the gene pool

00:43:12.680 --> 00:43:13.690
of humanity.

00:43:13.720 --> 00:43:14.880
Literally

00:43:15.040 --> 00:43:19.460
like a virus of love, you know,
it will just begin to spread.

00:43:19.490 --> 00:43:21.060
And it's

00:43:21.080 --> 00:43:23.820
non-denominational, it doesn't-- you know,
it's everywhere.

00:43:23.850 --> 00:43:26.940
It's in the weirdest places,
it's in, you know, the

00:43:26.970 --> 00:43:29.210
tiny little communities, because

00:43:29.240 --> 00:43:30.840
it's everywhere.

00:43:31.400 --> 00:43:34.400
It's not fixed on any chosen people,

00:43:34.960 --> 00:43:36.480
you know, as in the past.

00:43:38.720 --> 00:43:40.781
So it's going to wake up.

00:43:40.981 --> 00:43:46.140
You know, I always like that
one-liner that Jesus left behind him

00:43:46.170 --> 00:43:50.680
where he said, 'When I return,
I will return like a thief in the night,'

00:43:51.240 --> 00:43:53.580
you know, and I contemplated
that for many, many years,

00:43:53.610 --> 00:43:57.806
and one day I just saw that and I was
like, 'Oh, wow, yeah. It's coming,

00:43:58.006 --> 00:44:01.420
you can't stop it, it's secret,
it's hidden, it's everywhere.

00:44:01.450 --> 00:44:04.780
It's a thief in the night,
it's just going to arrive.'

00:44:04.810 --> 00:44:06.400
And it's this,

00:44:07.640 --> 00:44:09.820
you know, 'new human'
that we're talking about.

00:44:09.850 --> 00:44:13.500
This is the new human
that we've both seen.

00:44:13.530 --> 00:44:16.000
And I think many people are

00:44:16.040 --> 00:44:17.320
sensing,

00:44:17.400 --> 00:44:19.620
here already among us,

00:44:19.650 --> 00:44:23.500
in its potential, like you
mentioned the Buddhas and things.

00:44:23.530 --> 00:44:29.020
And one thing, probably that I loved more
than anything else in your book, Chris,

00:44:29.050 --> 00:44:35.260
is when you describe the future human,
and I was left with this image

00:44:35.290 --> 00:44:39.300
of all these Buddhas sitting down,
meditating and stuff,

00:44:39.330 --> 00:44:42.460
and then this one human
standing in the middle of them,

00:44:42.490 --> 00:44:45.660
standing on its own two feet,
and that was the future human.

00:44:45.690 --> 00:44:48.100
And
I thought-- you know, I feel like that's

00:44:48.130 --> 00:44:52.566
such an enduring,
iconic symbol of what's coming.

00:44:52.766 --> 00:44:53.766
Because

00:44:54.000 --> 00:44:57.460
we're no longer-- it's no longer
the journey of meditation and spiritual

00:44:57.480 --> 00:45:00.940
awakening, and the spiritual journey
and this awakening through transformation

00:45:00.970 --> 00:45:04.480
of the shadow,
suddenly that's come to an end,

00:45:04.920 --> 00:45:08.200
and suddenly that being is standing.

00:45:08.240 --> 00:45:11.880
You know, there's no practice anymore,
other than living.

00:45:12.320 --> 00:45:13.680
And then

00:45:14.240 --> 00:45:15.600
that human

00:45:15.840 --> 00:45:19.240
really begins a new humanity, because

00:45:19.400 --> 00:45:22.073
there's no more awakening process.

00:45:22.273 --> 00:45:25.140
There are layers and layers of creative

00:45:25.170 --> 00:45:29.620
expansion, always infinite
creative expansion.

00:45:29.650 --> 00:45:31.180
And there's playfulness.

00:45:31.200 --> 00:45:32.640
And there's

00:45:34.040 --> 00:45:36.680
new layers of engagement

00:45:37.920 --> 00:45:41.280
within the construct of reality.

00:45:41.480 --> 00:45:44.460
You know, all these levels and dimensions

00:45:44.490 --> 00:45:47.860
and fields that we can explore, you know,

00:45:47.880 --> 00:45:48.960
through

00:45:49.400 --> 00:45:50.580
a new way.

00:45:50.610 --> 00:45:53.210
And what I really see

00:45:53.240 --> 00:45:54.960
clearly is

00:45:56.040 --> 00:46:00.051
as that's-- as the age
of suffering comes to an end,

00:46:00.251 --> 00:46:03.600
you know, we have a new field,
and it's bliss.

00:46:04.320 --> 00:46:05.580
You know, we have learned enough

00:46:05.610 --> 00:46:10.860
from suffering, now is our chance
and opportunity to learn from bliss,

00:46:10.890 --> 00:46:14.640
because bliss
is the other side of suffering.

00:46:15.080 --> 00:46:17.380
It's the same, it's almost the same thing.

00:46:17.410 --> 00:46:19.980
It's all that suffering leads to bliss.

00:46:20.010 --> 00:46:22.620
And yet bliss is just the other

00:46:22.640 --> 00:46:26.500
-- it's like the white hole to the black
hole, you know, it's like you go through

00:46:26.530 --> 00:46:30.680
a black hole, you come out the other side,
there's this white hole

00:46:31.320 --> 00:46:37.260
and it's-- and it has as much
depth and juice as suffering does.

00:46:37.280 --> 00:46:38.320
You know, so

00:46:38.520 --> 00:46:41.380
there's a similarity to them

00:46:41.410 --> 00:46:45.900
but it's a new muse that humanity has.

00:46:45.930 --> 00:46:49.740
So when we sit in that bliss,

00:46:49.770 --> 00:46:53.980
and we move through that bliss,
we're moving through

00:46:54.010 --> 00:46:58.980
the highest aspects of our consciousness,
and that then has to all be explored,

00:46:59.000 --> 00:47:02.460
all of it. Because bliss, like suffering,
has layer, upon layer, upon layer,

00:47:02.490 --> 00:47:06.880
upon layer, upon layer and dimension,
and dimension, and dimension.

00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:11.380
And there's a whole epoch needed
again, just to explore bliss.

00:47:11.400 --> 00:47:12.480
So

00:47:12.600 --> 00:47:14.400
that's why, in a way,

00:47:14.640 --> 00:47:16.420
if you can hold that

00:47:16.450 --> 00:47:21.960
in your heart and your mind
as we move through these very difficult

00:47:23.000 --> 00:47:26.940
decades ahead, and
century-- centuries,

00:47:26.970 --> 00:47:31.240
perhaps few centuries - I agree,
by the way, 21st century

00:47:32.360 --> 00:47:35.500
is-- seems to be the one,
the next century,

00:47:35.530 --> 00:47:38.800
you know, seems to be the one
- and, you know, remember that's us.

00:47:42.200 --> 00:47:43.380
You know, like, we'll be there.

00:47:43.400 --> 00:47:46.068
And I mean, you know, I say to people,
'You don't want to miss this.'

00:47:46.268 --> 00:47:47.460
You know, like,
people saying, like,

00:47:47.490 --> 00:47:51.660
'This is my last incarnation.' Okay, well,
make sure you come back for that one,

00:47:51.690 --> 00:47:55.840
because you don't want to do all
